---
title: Southern-Inspired Chorizo Gravy with Roasted Potatoes and Peppers and Charred Corn Salad
description: This riff on classic Southern sausage gravy will hit the mark for those craving comfort with a Tex-Mex spin. You'll smother potatoes and peppers with a delectable chorizo gravy and toasted ciabatta comes alongside for mandatory dipping. A tomato, charred corn and feta salad is the perfect way to cut the richness between bites.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sauce-au-chorizo-inspiree-du-sud-5cf2f714.jpg
